# Docker build context allowlist.
#
# Exclude everything, re-include Docker build inputs, then exclude
# generated and local-only files that Docker would otherwise keep.

# Exclude everything by default.
*

# Docker build inputs.
!Dockerfile
!requirements.txt
!src/
!src/**

# Keep generated or local-only files out after re-including `src/`.
src/**/__pycache__/
src/**/*.py[cod]
src/**/*.egg-info/
src/simple_test.py
